{"tid":147003,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我發現我男朋友有SP。","createTime":"2017-03-07T14:13:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-07T18:28:00.000Z","uid":60491,"like":3,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0af41d78d5127f4c617dfc2181e2b9b54143d128","tid":147003,"uid":60491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T14:13:56.000Z","msg":"好大打擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一直覺得佢好乖乖仔，又好就我，對我屋企人都好好，我以為自己好幸福。<br />\n<br />\n我知道佢今日放假，偷偷地上左佢屋企。個陣仲早，佢訓緊我無嘈醒佢，點知俾我無意中見到有個女仔whatsapp 佢「今日邊度等呀bb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？」<br />\n<br />\n於是我即刻質問佢，原來喺我地未一齊之前，佢已經有個SP，直至而家。<br />\n<br />\n我即刻同佢講分手，但佢喊住留我，話佢一定會同個SP講清楚。<br />\n但其實我唔單止原諒唔到佢咁對我，更加接受唔到佢有過SP，覺得好污糟<br />\n不過見佢咁我又好心軟，所以而家好亂！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c1b59816ad0a0b8b6edde06919730d5dfb3f187","tid":147003,"uid":11598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T14:14:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 賤貨"},{"pid":"42f76456684a4fcc9e8774bb0743ee1f23959cdb","tid":147003,"uid":77139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T14:15:27.000Z","msg":"啱呀"},{"pid":"3259ac742317003d3d317d05089d751f1b6ee8d3","tid":147003,"uid":60491,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T14:17:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 賤貨</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢鬧我賤貨唔緊要<br />\n點解要搵SP"},{"pid":"dadc0bd428e0deec56212051d045de2d07b94793","tid":147003,"uid":60491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T14:17:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啱呀</blockquote><br />\n啱乜鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hk